parameters: Hey, thank you for coming after seeing the flyer.
Who the hell are you guys? Are you friends?
Are you all safe?! I've come to help!

Tch, you're getting in the way just when we were
about to have some fun.

Ah, I see. Well then, shall we consider that fun
time over? I wouldn't mind doing something even
more enjoyable for you.

Oh, it's you? Hmmm...? Those eyes of yours are
telling lies, aren't they?
You guys! I'm gonna fuck you up!!!
See, it's become even more fun. I'm not lying.
I'm glad, it looks like both of you are safe.
Are you okay...! I'm glad you're alive...

...I'm sorry, Luther... I narrowly escaped
death... I'm still fine, but... she...
Understood. Can we use the emergency portal now?

Yes, I'm fine... Thank you so much... Luther and
the magical girl over there...

Thank you, Konoha-san. I couldn't have saved
everyone on my own. You are our hope... ours!
What's going on? It's nothing special, huh~?

Well, whatever. It's too much of a hassle to kill
all you guys anyway.
Now, let the fun time begin~
